Figure 1: The processing pipeline of the two-stream CNN [24], which has demonstrated competitive video classification
performance. ‚ÄúConv.‚Äù indicates ‚ÄúConvolution‚Äù and ‚ÄúFC‚Äù is the abbreviation of ‚ÄúFully Connected‚Äù. Our evaluations in this
