Kai Kang1,2 Hongsheng Li2,? Tong Xiao1,2 Wanli Ouyang2,5 Junjie Yan3 Xihui Liu4 Xiaogang Wang2,?
1Shenzhen Key Lab of Comp. Vis. & Pat. Rec., Shenzhen Institutes of Advanced Technology, CAS, China
