Artifact Reduction
Haofu Liao1 (␀), Zhimin Huo2, William J. Sehnert2, Shaohua Kevin Zhou3,
and Jiebo Luo1
1 Department of Computer Science, University of Rochester, Rochester, USA
hliao6@cs.rochester.edu
